  "instructions": [
    "1. Heat oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "2. Add onions and bell peppers; cook until tender, about 5 minutes.",
    "3. Add mushrooms; cook until they release their moisture and start to brown, about 5 minutes.",
    "4. Stir in tomato paste and cook for 1-2 minutes.",
    "5. Add spicy sauce and stir to combine.",
    "6. Cook for an additional 2-3 minutes, until the sauce has thickened.",
    "7. Serve hot, garnished with parsley.",
    "8. Serve with a side of bread or over rice, if desired."
